oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Little girl with doll
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Hazel Brown posed next to a chair. She is holding a doll and there is a toy dog and a toy horse at her feet. There is a quilt behind her and she has a large bow in her hair.
